At BuildCalc, we respect user privacy and are committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy explains how information is handled when using the app.

1. Information We Collect

BuildCalc does not collect any personal or sensitive information such as:

Name

Phone number

Email address

Location data

The app may store some data locally on the user's device only, including:

App settings (language, currency, theme)

Calculation results

Usage history

All data remains on the device and is never transmitted to external servers.

2. How We Use Information

Stored data is used solely to:

Improve user experience

Save calculation results

Remember user preferences

No data is used for advertising or marketing purposes.

3. Data Sharing

We confirm that:

No data is shared with third parties

No data is sold or exchanged

No analytics or tracking services are currently used

4. PDF Export

When exporting results as a PDF file:

The file is generated locally on the device

No files are uploaded online

The app does not retain any copies

5. Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect user data by:

Using secure local storage

Avoiding unnecessary permissions

Not using unrequired external connections

6. Children‚Äôs Privacy

BuildCalc is not intended for children under the age of 13 and does not knowingly collect personal data from them.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page. Continued use of the app implies acceptance of the updated policy.

